Hi Benjamin Barber,
=C2=A0
Miso announced today a new nationwide support partnership with AwesomeOS, a=
 proven leader in multilingual technical robotics support and customer expe=
rience operations. This collaboration expands our ability to deliver top-qu=
ality 24/7 virtual customer support for our Flippy Fry Station AI robots as=
 we work to scale their deployments across the country.

Rebecca Davis, Miso=E2=80=99s Vice President of Operations, said, =E2=80=9C=
As Flippy=E2=80=99s adoption continues to grow, world-class support becomes=
 just as critical as world-class technology. AwesomeOS allows us to scale c=
ustomer support with speed, consistency, and nationwide reach.=E2=80=9D Dav=
is added, =E2=80=9CJust as partners like NVIDIA, Uber AI, and Amazon have h=
elped to strengthened our AI and cloud infrastructure, AwesomeOS strengthen=
s the human layer of our platform=E2=80=94ensuring customers get fast, reli=
able support in the languages and time zones they operate in.=E2=80=9D

Lexi Schneider, AwesomeOS=E2=80=99 Head of North American Marketing, said, =
=E2=80=9CMiso=E2=80=99s vision for intelligent, connected restaurant kitche=
ns aligns directly with how we think about global customer experience at sc=
ale. This partnership reflects a shared commitment to reliability, operatio=
nal excellence, and long-term growth as Flippy deployments expand.=E2=80=9D

Why it matters:

24/7, Multilingual Coverage
Flippy=E2=80=99s restaurant operators get real-time support across regions,=
 languages, and service hours.

Faster, More Cost-Efficient Scale
Partnering with a proven support team allows us to expand our support capac=
ity without building expensive internal teams=E2=80=94helping control costs=
, while boosting quality.

Stronger Customer Experience
Faster resolution times improve uptime, operator confidence, and long-term =
retention for our products.

